- what_is_diaspora = '<h3>what is diaspora*?</h3> |
    <p>diaspora* is an awesome decentralized open source social network full of really cool people. Instead of being owned and controlled by a single corporation, all the pods (servers) in the diaspora* network are totally independent and controlled usually by single individuals.</p> |
    <p> The project, which is run by a community of volunteers, builds the software which is free to use by anyone. You can easily run a pod yourself too, or if you don\'t want to, check out some of the open pods and go create an account!</p> |
    <div> |
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://diasporafoundation.org" target="_blanc">More information</a> |
        <a class="btn btn-success" href="http://pods.jasonrobinson.me">Find a pod</a> |
    </div>' |
