- about_this_pod = '<h3>about this pod</h3> |
    <p>I Like Toast is maintained by <a href="https://iliketoast.net/u/jaywink">Jason Robinson</a> as a free service to the diaspora* community. |
    Occasionally invitations will be closed to make sure the pod keep runnings smoothly, but when invitations are open, anyone is welcome |
    to create an account. By creating an account you agree to the <a href="https://iliketoast.net/terms">terms of service and privacy policy</a>. Please |
    read these carefully before creating an account.</p> |
    <h3>code version</h3> |
    <p>This pod runs on the development branch of the diaspora* source code. <b>This means things will occasionally break</b>, though every effort will |
    made to make sure this doesn\'t happen often. Changelogs of new features and fixes will be posted to the |
    <a href="https://iliketoast.net/u/podmin">podmin account</a>, so it makes sense to follow that.</p> |
    <div> |
        <a class="btn btn-info" href="https://iliketoast.net/terms">Terms of Service</a> |
        <a class="btn btn-success" href="http://iliketoast.net/u/podmin">Pod news</a> |
    </div>' |
